<troubleshooting id="troubleshooting-6951" xml:lang="en-us" class="- topic/topic troubleshooting/troubleshooting "><title class="- topic/title ">Unable to Start Application on this device: Appium directory is invalid</title><troublebody class="- topic/body troubleshooting/troublebody "><troubleSolution class="- topic/bodydiv troubleshooting/troubleSolution "><cause class="- topic/section troubleshooting/cause "><p class="- topic/p ">Katalon Studio cannot locate the provided Appium directory.</p></cause><remedy class="- topic/section troubleshooting/remedy "><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Double check your Appium directory to make sure it should be as shown below:</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">For Windows: (<uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-windows" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> &gt; <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-katalon-studio-preferences" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> &gt; <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-mobile" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Appium Directory</uicontrol>).</info><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock ">C:\Users\&lt;Username&gt;\AppData\Roaming\npm\node_modules\appium</codeblock></info><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">For MacOS/Linux: (<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Katalon Studio</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-preferences" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> &gt; <uicontrol conkeyref="ks-UI-text/ks-ui-mobile" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol "/> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Appium Directory</uicontrol>).</info><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock ">/usr/local/lib/node_modules/appium</codeblock></info></step></steps></remedy></troubleSolution></troublebody></troubleshooting>